Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:02:00.59,sign_3520_34_Episode_One__The,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)\pos(110,65)\b1\fs14}Episode Four \NMy Image?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:02.22,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a pamphlet \Nfor the photography club?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.10,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.85,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm compiling photos taken \Nby each of the club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:09.22,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I really like your photos, Tanigawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Like the one you sent me the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.84,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to pull it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.76,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:24.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But... are you sure you \Nwant me... to be your model?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:29.26,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You were the first \Nperson to come to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.92,sign_3619_15_Roubai_Academy_P,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,20)\fs10}Roubai Academy Photography Club Introductory Pamphlet Production Guidelines \N{\fs8}Pamphlet Concept \N{\fs18}"Friends"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But do I actually have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.93,sign_3835_18_Drama_Club_This_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,20)}Drama\NClub\NThis\NWay {right}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.93,sign_3835_18_Drama_Club_This_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(15,120)\c&H303C46&}Seeking\NNew\N Members {left}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:47.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I'm gonna give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:50.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Prez?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.47,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it'll be good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.14,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're drawing attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.86,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,A wide range of experiences \Nis crucial to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:16.22,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,You should make use of anything \Nthat'll contribute to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:27.01,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,My club president said it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.80,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.89,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I'm all sweaty, \Nsince I ran to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.01,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:43.04,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure I should just wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.94,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want to capture you \Nin your natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:02.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Togano-san joined the basketball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.22,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.27,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.79,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nawashiro-san and Washio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Kamimoku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.11,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't everyone amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,All of those clubs looked so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:53.97,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta work hard in mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.06,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.62,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.97,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The tea ceremony club is on break today,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.84,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,so they made an exception to let me use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.27,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go ahead and get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:16.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.77,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.80,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I look so stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.01,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It might be because I'm \Nnot used to the settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.77,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to try a few different things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.76,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.93,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Try brushing your hair back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.04,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:54.96,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.57,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Now look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.78,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's too close, Tanigawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.41,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,They look really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:18.55,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,But they don't quite look like \Nthe image of you in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:21.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The image of me in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.08,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.59,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're getting \Nfarther and farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew you'd think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:45.09,sign_9593_66_Close_up_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(30,80)}CLOSE-UP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:45.09,sign_9593_66_Close_up_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\an8\bord2\fs10\pos(115,80)}FUKUMOTO MIKI\N\N{\c&H41CFD4&\fs8}- BEHIND THE STAGE -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:44.63,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... that was all just \Nme copying Miki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.48,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't any help at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:54.40,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,No, I got lots of great pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.74,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick a few from these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.21,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akebi-san, watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.07,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.14,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.86,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Are you oka—oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.95,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-chan! Tanigawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.49,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Just startled me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.22,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san, your uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.29,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not okay at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.04,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Sorry! Sorry! Oh, man, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.38,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll come off. I'll just wash \Nit as soon as I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.88,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.40,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The Mangetsu Dorm is close by, and it \Nhas washing machines! Let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.71,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mangetsu Dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.07,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the dorm we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.82,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! We're almost done with practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.34,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Give me just a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.99,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san, you're welcome to come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Want to, Tanigawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.94,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... ask my mom, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:01.44,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I should do that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.81,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I've never gone anywhere but \Nstraight home after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:07.64,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.73,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Something's making a lot of noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's all frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,They're glad there's so \Nmuch water in the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.25,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.80,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what were you two doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.94,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.80,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Akebi-san to model for some photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.49,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Cool! That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't a good model at all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.47,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.27,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like the perfect \Nphoto subject to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:48.70,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is my image, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.89,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Image?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:53.99,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to explain it, either.
