Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.89,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-3, Usagihara! I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.83,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.53,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I brought two visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.03,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Just write the time and your names here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write your name, too, Tanigawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.61,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.45,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.90,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the one they used before \Nswitching to the current one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.30,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,I wore it, too. That takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.38,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,But why this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.57,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
