Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.69,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.58,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Yuwa-san's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.87,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,She was a student of mine! \NWhat a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.68,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:34.55,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,She was constantly breaking the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.17,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,But students and teachers \Nalike still loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.67,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Akebi-chan is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:52.17,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't expecting to hear a \Nfun story like that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:52.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:54.70,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know about that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.06,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I should tell Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.44,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, in addition to Mangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:04.25,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Roubai also has the Soshin Dorm \Nfor high school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:08.33,top,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to use the name of a flower that \Nblooms in a different season than the roubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.87,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. They haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.20,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let anyone see \Nsomething this embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.27,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And on both feet, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.08,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:14.86,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:19.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Your socks got \Nall muddy too, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.10,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,This is our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.94,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And Kizaki-san's is next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaki-san! Should we say hi to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.25,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's in charge of giving \Nthe dorm announcements today,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.07,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,so she's probably not in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.86,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.98,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.61,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty roomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.63,sign_15636_161_Math_I,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-31.61\fax-0.42\pos(469,88)}Math I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.31,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Miki-chan's CD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.31,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:03.92,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Neko-chan's my roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.37,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,We won't wake Kamimoku-san, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.88,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.35,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,All the noise in the \Nworld won't wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:15.30,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the way she looked doing \Nkyudo earlier was just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.76,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She really is just like a cat,\N sleeping all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.03,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.78,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Get changed and make yourselves comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:26.39,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I didn't bring my PE \Nclothes to change into.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.79,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no problem. I was gonna \Nlend you mine, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.94,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Tanigawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:31.52,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.96,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:41.79,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll just have to get \NAkebi-chan all dolled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.80,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really, anything's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.80,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! I had just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:52.16,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Akebi-chan, take all that stuff off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.51,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.21,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it on impulse after \Nseeing it in a magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.12,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't really work on me,\N and it's too tight anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.33,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.51,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,it'll look perfect on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.83,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There you go! Oh, you need socks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:31.83,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You've done it again. You look just \Nas good as the magazine model.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.82,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty, I'm afraid \NI'll get it dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:44.65,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I might've \Ngone to school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.90,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.88,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wash that stuff before it stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.60,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.49,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.51,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.77,main,Dorm Resident 1,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.63,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. This'll handle the drying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.95,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.38,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.02,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ready to head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.02,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.24,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.02,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two like sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:36.74,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make us a snack. \NYou guys can hang out and chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You can cook, too, Usagihara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.16,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Only those of us in charge of the \Ndorm's chores can use the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.18,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.38,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:13.68,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.69,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.08,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.55,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Did you make all of these yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:24.08,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.07,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.51,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.78,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Really? If anything doesn't suit \Nyour taste, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.31,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:39.00,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can you even talk with your \Ncheeks that stuffed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Buh der fho nudd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.19,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start cooking, Usagihara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.93,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.01,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Usagihara-san, do you have snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.09,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:00.54,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akebi-san and Tanigawa-san. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Nawashiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.79,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,We came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.72,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.49,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Butter cookies today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.36,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:14.36,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan just finished practice, \Nand she says she's starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.92,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and there's still \Nsome time before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.13,top,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.57,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Washio-san lives here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.74,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.76,main,Dorm Resident 2,0000,0000,0000,,Usagihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.31,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, I've got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.93,top,Dorm Resident 2,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for always sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.78,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And she's from a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.04,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.22,top,Dorm Resident 2,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.75,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.13,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tougeguchi-san. Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.68,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,These are for you, if you want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.31,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.62,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Tougeguchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.49,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Y'almost look like an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.01,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.16,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Usagihara-san's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.43,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She's already friends with \Nso many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.22,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta ask for more recipes \Nbefore I run out of material.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.20,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Material?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.08,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,My family runs a Western sweets shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.17,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why they taste \Nprofessionally made!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:12.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. You're quite \Nthe flatterer, Tanigawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite like that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:21.85,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdly enough, when I lived at home, \NI had zero interest in making sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:26.06,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I only handled sales and, when my parents \Nwere there, cleaning up the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.72,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So how do you know the recipes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.20,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I call home and ask for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.72,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I've screwed up half of the \Nones I've tried, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.48,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,When I introduced myself to the dorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.35,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wore this and said, \N"I'm Usagihara!" And it fell flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:43.81,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to break the ice,\N and it totally backfired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What? But why? It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:51.15,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Turns out the only thing that works is \Nshowing your underwear, like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a huge mistake. \NPlease forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.28,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.80,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So the idea I came up with \Nto save my reputation was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.89,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,making sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That was good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.76,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Dorm life comes with so many rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.92,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to buy anything, \Nyou have to put in a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:11.41,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So some of the girls were saying it'd be nice\N if we could at least be free to eat sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:14.96,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it might suck \Nhaving limits on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.33,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Everyone here felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:21.48,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So, since I have the freedom to \Nbuy food and use the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.18,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That kinda sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.97,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.20,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They all give me their pocket \Nchange to buy ingredients with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:34.53,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys asked, I'd make \Nsome and take them to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.47,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That would make me really happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.49,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But what impresses me is that \Nyou can actually make sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.39,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't make stuff like that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly great at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:49.40,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I help my mom make dinner \Nsometimes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.87,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What a good daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.87,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna try it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:56.42,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If even I can do it, \Nyou'll pick it up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.63,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure it's okay for me to make these?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.84,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pay no attention to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:06.47,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get a great photo opportunity \Nlike this every day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.47,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure this comes \Nout super delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.65,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You put the butter in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.72,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to stir so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:16.41,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I use?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.99,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You can pick a plate later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.98,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.49,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.97,main,Kei; Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.01,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.12,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.51,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,A cracker made of charcoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crêpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:47.51,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really are bad at this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:51.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry it turned out like \Nthis after you helped me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:54.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I wasn't a very good teacher, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.57,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I've done today has gone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.14,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:02.70,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda relieved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.91,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were this perfect \Ngirl who could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.98,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you better next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I can come over again some—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.34,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.11,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I ate two or three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:30.62,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You mean you ate all of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.37,top,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.01,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if you gain weight, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:42.32,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akebi-chan's burp woke up Neko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:46.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did not! It was you laughing so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.66,main,Neko,0000,0000,0000,,Good... morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.70,main,Komichi; Kei; Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
