Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.60,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! All the mud came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.15,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda warm, too! It feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.13,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Akebi-san, where are your socks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:11.15,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nthey weren't in the wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.93,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. They weren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.70,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was too embarrassed to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.24,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I got to see so \Nmany sides of you today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.45,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,nothing you do is gonna surprise me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.48,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tanigawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.44,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't take pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.88,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Usagihara-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:53.37,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a better idea \Nof what your image is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does that mean I'm a slob?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.11,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:02.13,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Though... you do have a \Nbit of a clumsy side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.23,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The Akebi-san I see at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:08.13,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,and the Akebi-san who tried \Nso hard at cooking today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:12.37,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,They're both straightforward and \Nhonest, and always giving their all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:16.98,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,So I think these pictures \Ndepict that Akebi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:23.11,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you always wave at \Nthe bus on the way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:23.91,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:25.31,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.21,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't see inside it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.63,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bus I take to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:36.67,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,If you run that much every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:39.19,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,it's no wonder you wear holes in your socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.87,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi! Kao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
